Algutsboda samt kommin. i Algutsbo-da, kyrkoh. i Ölmstad sed. 42. Ordf. i kyrkostämman, folksk :styr., barnav:-ndn. Röda korskretsen samt hembygds-fören.
translated: Johansson, Josef Holmfrid Emanuel, clergyman, Brötjemark, born 4/6/02 in Bäckaby, Jönköping county, son of Johannes J. and Elise Johansson. Married in 1931 to Eira Karlsson. Children: Staffan b. 1936, Ulla b. 1940. He took his baccalaureate in Lund in 1924, theological bachelor's degree in 1926, theological licentiate, practical theology degree and was ordained as a priest for Växjö diocese in 1931. He has been assistant vicar in Oskar and Örsjö, and vicar in Algutsboda and Nyemåla. He was appointed parish priest in Algutsboda and then in Ölmstad in 1942. He served as chairman of the church assembly, the school board, the child welfare committee, the Red Cross district and the local heritage association.
